## 🔧 Configuration

### Variables d'environnement (.env)

```env
# Apify
APIFY_TOKEN=your_apify_token_here

# APIs tierces (optionnel)
PROXYCURL_API_KEY=your_proxycurl_key
SCRAPIN_API_KEY=your_scrapin_key

# Scraping
MAX_REQUESTS_PER_SOURCE=50
HEADLESS_BROWSER=true
TIMEOUT=30000

# Export
EXPORT_FORMAT=json,csv
OUTPUT_PATH=./outputs/
```

